{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 15,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الحِجۡرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Hijr",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Rock",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 99,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 1803,
        "text": "艾利夫，俩目，拉[阿拉伯语三个字母的音译，唯安拉最知道其意]。这些是经典[《古兰经》]的经文，是明白的《古兰经》[的经文]。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1804,
        "text": "不信仰者也许会希望自己原是归顺者[穆斯林]。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1805,
        "text": "你让他们吃喝玩乐吧！你让他们被妄想[注]迷惑吧！他们不久将知道。",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1806,
        "text": "凡是我所毁灭的城市，它都有一个定期。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1807,
        "text": "任何一个民族都不会在其定期前消亡，也不会延缓。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1808,
        "text": "他们[不信仰者]说：“受赐教诲[《古兰经》]的人[穆圣]啊！你真是个疯子。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1809,
        "text": "你为什么不昭示我们一些天使呢？假如你是诚实者。”",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1810,
        "text": "我只依真理降示天使，否则[如果我降示天使]，他们将不被缓刑。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1811,
        "text": "我确已降示教诲[《古兰经》]，我就是教诲的保护者。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1812,
        "text": "在你之前，我确已派遣许多使者去教化昔日的各宗派[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1813,
        "text": "每当一位使者来临他们，他们总是嘲笑他。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1814,
        "text": "我如此使它[多神崇拜]进入犯罪者的心中。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1815,
        "text": "他们不相信[我的]教诲[《古兰经》]，尽管前人[不信仰安拉而遭惩罚]的先例已逝去。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1816,
        "text": "假如我为他们从天上开一道门，他们必定从那道门开始登天，",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1817,
        "text": "他们必定说：“我们眼花缭乱了，不，我们是被迷惑的民众。”",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 262,
        "ruku": 218,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1818,
        "text": "我确已在天空创造许多宫座，并为观察者装饰它。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1819,
        "text": "我保护它远离一切被驱逐的恶魔的侵犯，",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1820,
        "text": "唯窃听的恶魔例外，[因为]他有明显的火焰追赶着。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1821,
        "text": "我展开了大地，在上面稳固地安置群山，并在其中生产出各种均量之物。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1822,
        "text": "我在其中为你们和你们不能供养者[牲畜与野兽等]创造了许多生活资料。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1823,
        "text": "万物在我这里都有贮存处，我只依定量降下它。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1824,
        "text": "我派遣风[给浓云]受精，然后，我从云中降下雨水，供你们饮用，你们绝不是雨水的贮存者。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1825,
        "text": "我的确能使死者生，能使生者死[注]。我是万物的继承者。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1826,
        "text": "我确知你们已逝去的先辈，也确知你们的现辈和后辈。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1827,
        "text": "你的主必将集合他们。他确是最睿智的，全知的[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 219,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1828,
        "text": "我确已用黑色的粘土创造人。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1829,
        "text": "以前，我曾用火焰创造精灵。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1830,
        "text": "当时，你的主对天使们说：“我将用黑色的粘土创造一个人[阿丹]。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1831,
        "text": "当我造完他并把灵魂吹入他[阿丹]的体内时，你们当服从他。”",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1832,
        "text": "所有天使都服从了，",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1833,
        "text": "唯伊怖里斯例外，他拒绝同天使们一起服从。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 263,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1834,
        "text": "他[安拉]说：“伊怖里斯啊！你为什么不同天使们一起服从呢？”",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1835,
        "text": "他[伊怖里斯]说：“我不能服从你用黑色粘土创造的人。”",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1836,
        "text": "他[安拉]说：“你从这里[乐园]出去吧！你是被驱逐的。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1837,
        "text": "你必将常遭谴责，直到审判日。”",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1838,
        "text": "他[伊怖里斯]说：“我的主啊！求你宽延我到他们[人类]被复活的那一天。”",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1839,
        "text": "他[安拉]说：“你被宽延了，",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1840,
        "text": "直到注定的时日。”",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1841,
        "text": "他[伊怖里斯]说：“我的主啊！由于你让我离开了正道，我必将在大地上诱惑他们[人类]，必将诱骗他们所有人，",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1842,
        "text": "他们中你所特选的仆人除外。”",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1843,
        "text": "他[安拉]说：“这是我该维持的正道。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1844,
        "text": "你绝没有能力对付我的仆人们[真信士]，但追随你的迷误者例外。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1845,
        "text": "火狱确是他们全体约定的地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1846,
        "text": "火狱有七道门，每道门都将收容他们中被指定的一部分人[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 220,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1847,
        "text": "敬畏者必将进住乐园和泉水旁。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1848,
        "text": "[有话声对他们说]：“你们平平安安进入乐园吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1849,
        "text": "我将消除他们[敬畏者]心中[彼此间可能存在]的怨恨，他们将兄弟般面对面坐在宝椅上。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1850,
        "text": "他们在乐园里既不会疲倦，也不会被逐走。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1851,
        "text": "你当告诉我的仆人们：“我确是最宽恕的，特慈的。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 105,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1852,
        "text": "我的刑罚确是痛苦的刑罚。”",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1853,
        "text": "你当告诉他们关于伊布拉欣的客人们[天使们]的故事。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 264,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1854,
        "text": "当时，他们[天使们]进去见他。他们[天使们]说：“求主赐你平安！”他[伊布拉欣]说：“我们非常害怕你们。”",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1855,
        "text": "他们说：“你不要害怕，我们必将以一个精明的男孩向你报喜[注]。”",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1856,
        "text": "他说：“你们在我年迈时还给我报喜吗？你们要给我报什么喜呢？”",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1857,
        "text": "他们说：“我们依真理向你报喜，所以，你不要绝望。”",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1858,
        "text": "他[伊布拉欣]说：“除迷误者外，谁会对他的主[安拉]的恩惠绝望呢？”",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1859,
        "text": "他[伊布拉欣]说：“使者们[天使们]啊！你们的使命是什么？”",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1860,
        "text": "他们说：“我们奉命来惩治一伙犯罪的民众，",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1861,
        "text": "但鲁特的家人除外，我们一定把他们全部救出，",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1862,
        "text": "但他的妻子例外。[安拉说]：“我已注定她[鲁特的妻子]同留在后面的人们一起[被毁灭]。”",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 221,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1863,
        "text": "当使者们[天使们]来到鲁特的家里时，",
        "numberInSurah": 61,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1864,
        "text": "他说：“你们是一群陌生人。”",
        "numberInSurah": 62,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1865,
        "text": "他们说：“不，我们给你带来了他们所怀疑的[刑罚]，",
        "numberInSurah": 63,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1866,
        "text": "我们给你带来了真理[你的族人要被毁灭的消息]，我们所讲的都是实话。",
        "numberInSurah": 64,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1867,
        "text": "你带着你的家人在五更出走吧！你当跟在他们后面，你们中任何人都不要回头看。你们到你们所被命令的地方去吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 65,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1868,
        "text": "我让他知道这个判决：这些人[犯罪者]将在早晨被根绝。",
        "numberInSurah": 66,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1869,
        "text": "城里人欣然来到[鲁特的家里]。",
        "numberInSurah": 67,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1870,
        "text": "他[鲁特]说：“这些是我的客人，你们不要让我丢脸。",
        "numberInSurah": 68,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1871,
        "text": "你们当敬畏安拉，你们不要让我受羞辱。”",
        "numberInSurah": 69,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1872,
        "text": "他们[城里人]说：“难道我们没有禁止你同外人交往吗？”",
        "numberInSurah": 70,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 265,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1873,
        "text": "他[鲁特]说：“这些是我的女儿[本族人之女]，假如你们一定要做。”",
        "numberInSurah": 71,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1874,
        "text": "以你[穆圣]的寿命发誓，他们[不相信你的使命者]必将在他们的陶醉中更加盲从。",
        "numberInSurah": 72,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1875,
        "text": "恐怖声在拂晓时袭击了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 73,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1876,
        "text": "我使那座城市天翻地覆，我降下烧过的陶土般的石块惩罚他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 74,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1877,
        "text": "对能思考的人们，此中确有许多迹象。",
        "numberInSurah": 75,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1878,
        "text": "那座城市就在[麦加至叙利亚的]大路旁。",
        "numberInSurah": 76,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1879,
        "text": "对信士们，此中确有一种迹象。",
        "numberInSurah": 77,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1880,
        "text": "丛林的居民[如安拉派遣舒阿布圣人去教化的马德亚人等]确是不义者。",
        "numberInSurah": 78,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1881,
        "text": "我惩罚了他们。这两个地方都在平坦的大道上。",
        "numberInSurah": 79,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 222,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1882,
        "text": "石谷的居民确已不信仰使者们[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 80,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1883,
        "text": "我曾赐予他们许多迹象，但他们总是背弃它。",
        "numberInSurah": 81,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1884,
        "text": "他们曾凿山为屋，以为可以安居。",
        "numberInSurah": 82,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1885,
        "text": "但恐怖声在拂晓时袭击了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 83,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1886,
        "text": "他们过去所做的一切对他们无益了。",
        "numberInSurah": 84,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1887,
        "text": "我只依真理创造天地万物。复活的时间肯定是要来临的，所以，你[穆圣]当宽容他们的过错[此节经文在圣战定为主命前已降示]。",
        "numberInSurah": 85,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1888,
        "text": "你的主确是创造万物者，全知者。",
        "numberInSurah": 86,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1889,
        "text": "我确已赐你常诵读的七节经文[注][即《古兰经》首章法提哈]和伟大的《古兰经》。",
        "numberInSurah": 87,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1890,
        "text": "对我赐予他们[不信仰者]中各种人享受的，你不要羡慕，不要替他们忧愁。你当谦和地对待信士们。",
        "numberInSurah": 88,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1891,
        "text": "你[穆圣]说：“我确是一位坦率的警告者。”",
        "numberInSurah": 89,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1892,
        "text": "正如我降给分裂者[基督教徒和犹太教徒]的一样。",
        "numberInSurah": 90,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 266,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1893,
        "text": "他们[分裂者]把《古兰经》分成许多部分[相信一部分，否认一部分]。",
        "numberInSurah": 91,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1894,
        "text": "以你的主发誓，我必将审问他们全体，",
        "numberInSurah": 92,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1895,
        "text": "必将审问他们所做的[恶行]。",
        "numberInSurah": 93,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1896,
        "text": "你当公开宣布你所奉到的命令，你当远避拜偶像者。",
        "numberInSurah": 94,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1897,
        "text": "我足以让你对付嘲笑者。",
        "numberInSurah": 95,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1898,
        "text": "他们[嘲笑者]既拜安拉，又拜其他神灵，他们不久将知道[崇拜神灵的后果]。",
        "numberInSurah": 96,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1899,
        "text": "我深知你为他们所说的胸中烦恼。",
        "numberInSurah": 97,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1900,
        "text": "你[穆圣]当赞美颂扬[注]你的主[安拉]，当同叩头者一起叩头。",
        "numberInSurah": 98,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 1901,
        "text": "你当崇拜你的主，直到不可避免的时刻[死亡]降临你[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 99,
        "juz": 14,
        "manzil": 3,
        "page": 267,
        "ruku": 223,
        "hizbQuarter": 106,
        "sajda": false
      }
